---
import Badge from "../../../components/Badge.astro";
import ProjectSection from "../../../components/ProjectSection.astro";
import Palette from "../../../icons/Palette.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import ProjectSpecs from "../../../components/ProjectSpecs.astro";
import Wand from "../../../icons/Wand.astro";
---

<ProjectSection
  title="Reimagining ILSA's Digital Presence"
  image="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/camilo-portfolio-77b8a.appspot.com/o/ILSA-Web-mockup.webp?alt=media&token=780054d4-1628-4e29-8652-29148ff403e5"
/>
<nav class="flex gap-2 mt-4 justify-center mb-4">
  <Badge
    content="Web Design"
    bgColor="bg-[#e46f4d]"
    textColor="text-[#4a241b]"
    darkBgColor="dark:bg-[#4a241b]"
    darkTextColor="dark:text-[#e46f4d]"
  />
  <Badge
    content="Image Editing"
    bgColor="bg-[#97acc6]"
    textColor="text-[#22282e]"
    darkBgColor="dark:bg-[#22282e]"
    darkTextColor="dark:text-[#97acc6]"
  />
  <Badge
    content="Illustration"
    bgColor="bg-[#f1cd71]"
    textColor="text-[#584b2c]"
    darkBgColor="dark:bg-[#584b2c]"
    darkTextColor="dark:text-[#f1cd71]"
  />
  <Badge
    content="WordPress"
    bgColor="bg-[#a3cda1]"
    textColor="text-[#293329]"
    darkBgColor="dark:bg-[#293329]"
    darkTextColor="dark:text-[#a3cda1]"
  />
</nav>

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-8">
  <div>
    <h3
      class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1e1e1e] dark:text-[#fafaf6] mb-6"
    >
      Project Details
    </h3>
    <p class="dark:text-gray-200">
      I served as the lead designer in creating the new website for ILSA, a
      non-governmental organization with over 40 years of experience focusing
      its efforts on supporting social movements, grassroots organizations, and
      disadvantaged sectors of society. This experience was rewarding, as it
      allowed me to apply my knowledge as a designer, utilizing Design Thinking
      as the primary methodology.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h3
      class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1e1e1e] dark:text-[#fafaf6] mb-6"
    >
      About the company
    </h3>
    <p class="dark:text-gray-200">
      ILSA, founded in 1978 as an NGO, focuses on alternative legal services and
      supporting social movements, grassroots organizations, and disadvantaged
      sectors. Initially operating in various Latin American countries, it has
      focused on Colombia since 1988.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<section>
  <ProjectSpecs
    rol="Web Designer, UI/UX"
    team="Viviana Tovar"
    duration="4 months"
    tools="Figma, Illustrator, Photoshop, WordPress"
  />
</section>

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 mt-10 gap-6">
  <div>
    <Image
      width="572"
      height="572"
      alt="ILSA-Web-mockup-1"
      class="w-full"
      src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/camilo-portfolio-77b8a.appspot.com/o/ILSA-Web-mockup-1.webp?alt=media&token=20977961-0397-4c6e-b91f-efd038073d62"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <h4
      class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1e1e1e] dark:text-[#fafaf6] mb-6"
    >
      Context
    </h4>
    <p class="dark:text-gray-200">
      As a starting point, I established an overall goal for the project,
      derived from an interview with ILSA's board of directors. During this
      conversation, the need to improve the visual representation of the website
      and ensure proper readability for visitors was identified. To address this
      issue, we chose to work with a simplified version of Design Thinking, with
      a special focus on the construction phase. This was due to the client's
      emphasis on the aesthetic aspect of the page.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h4
      class="text-lg md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1e1e1e] dark:text-[#fafaf6] mb-6"
    >
      Main Objective
    </h4>
    <p class="dark:text-gray-200">
      Provide an accurate, coherent, and aesthetically pleasing communication
      tool. Through a design process, establish a creative foundation to
      continue evolving the identity, hand in hand with the organization's
      growth.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h4
      class="text-lg md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1e1e1e] dark:text-[#fafaf6] mb-6"
    >
      Challenges
    </h4>
    <p class="dark:text-gray-200">
      ILSA lacked an online presence commensurate with its relevance in the
      sector. Additionally, it did not have a defined visual identity or
      communication language. Furthermore, the website was not optimized for SEO
      search engines.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<section>
  <h3
    class="flex gap-2 items-center text-3xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6 mt-6 dark:text-[#fafaf6]"
  >
    <Wand class="size-6" />Design Process
  </h3>
  <h4></h4>
